Switch post URLs from dated paths to /writing/:title/

Change permalink from /:year/:month/:day/:title/ to /writing/:title/ and
move the index page from /blog/ to /writing/ (nav and homepage links
updated to match). Add jekyll-redirect-from and redirect every old dated
URL (and /blog/) to its new location so existing links don't break.

